    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 is confirmed across all five COU operating points. The structured requirement set (https://uofa.net/synth/req/cpb-hemolysis-req-001) enumerates flow-rate range, hematocrit tolerance, and RH acceptance threshold; other safety properties are enumerated separately. The overall evidence package is judged sufficient to support regulatory submission for the Class II CPB device.",
